美国音乐产业收入创历史新高https://www.nme.com/news/music/revenue-in-us-music-industry-hits-all-time-high-3502824?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=revenue-in-us-music-industry-创历史新高Emma WilkesFri, 22 Sep 2023 19:36:40 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3502824 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="网络广播" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>上半年零售收入创历史新高，达 84 亿美元</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/revenue-in-us-music-industry-hits-all-time-high-3502824">美国音乐产业收入创历史新高的</a>消息首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="网络广播" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-527443240-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据美国唱片工业协会的<a href="https://www.riaa.com/riaa-mid-year-2023-revenue-report/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">年中收入报告</a>，美国音乐行业的收入已达到自唱片诞生以来的最高水平。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/vinyl-cassette-cd-sales-industry-3388285">实体音乐和黑胶唱片的销售目前正在蓬勃发展 - 但为什么呢？</a></strong></li></ul><p>零售收入（包括来自消费者流媒体服务的收入）跃升 9.3%，达到上半年历史新高 84 亿美元，而批发收入增长 8.3%，达到 53 亿美元。</p><p>流媒体收入较去年增长 10.3%，达到 70 亿美元，占美国音乐收入的 84%。 RIAA 明确指出，尽管付费订阅收入增长了 11%，达到 55 亿美元，但付费订阅总数仅增长了 6%。这可能是由于 Spotify 历史上首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-increases-subscription-prices-in-uk-and-us-first-time-3472555">提高了高级订阅的价格</a>。</p><p> Vinyl 的收入继续增长，实体格式的收入达到 2013 年以来的最高水平。然而，与流媒体收入相比，其数字相对较小，为 8.82 亿美元。总体而言，黑胶唱片占实体媒体销售额的 72%，其中 6.32 亿美元。去年黑胶唱片销量总计 2,300 万张，而 CD 销量为 1,500 万张。 </p><figure id="attachment_3485253" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3485253" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3485253" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl.jpg" alt="CU 手上搜索复古记录 - 图库照片。信用：盖蒂图片社" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Stock-image-of-vinyl-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3485253" class="wp-caption-text"> CU 手上搜索古董记录 – 图库照片。信用：盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>去年，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/global-music-market-worth-increased-by-18-per-cent-in-2021-to-19-5billion-3190762">2021 年全球音乐收入达到 90 年代有唱片以来的最高水平</a>，防弹少年<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">团 (BTS</a> )、阿黛尔 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">Adele</a> ) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift)</a>等艺术家的音乐贡献了 195 亿英镑的增长。</p><p>据行业贸易机构国际唱片业联合会 (IFPI) 在周二（3 月 22 日）发布的<a href="https://www.ifpi.org/ifpi-global-music-report-global-recorded-music-revenues-grew-18-5-in-2021/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一份新报告中称</a>，2021 年全球录制音乐收入增长了 18.5%，总计 196.3 亿英镑（259 亿美元），这主要得益于通过付费订阅流媒体的增加。</p><p>该报告指出，截至 2021 年底，付费订阅账户用户数量为 5.23 亿，高于 2020 年的 4.43 亿，增长了 21.9%，即 93.2 亿英镑（123 亿美元）。</p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/revenue-in-us-music-industry-hits-all-time-high-3502824">美国音乐产业收入创历史新高的</a>消息首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
斯佩克特分享充满活力的新单曲“Another Life” https://www.nme.com/news/music/spector-share-buoyant-new-single-another-life-3502818?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=spector-share-buoyant-new-single-another-lifeAnagricel Duran Fri, 22 Sep 2023 19:20:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3502818 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯佩克特。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队还将于 11 月开始英国巡演</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spector-share-buoyant-new-single-another-life-3502818">Spector 分享的新单曲《Another Life》</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯佩克特。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Spector.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/spector">斯佩克特</a>分享了他们即将发行的唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spector-share-hypnotic-new-single-the-notion-listen-3485165">Here Come the Early Nights</a> 》中的最新单曲《Another Life》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spectors-fred-macpherson-on-their-new-ep-mental-health-politics-and-sexual-abuse-2257812">Spector 的 Fred Macpherson 谈论他们的新 EP、心理健康、政治和打击性虐待</a></strong></li></ul><p>主唱 Fred Macpherson 在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时说道：“《Another Life》是《Here Come the Early Nights》中最乐观的歌曲之一，但在专辑的日落宇宙中仍然有意义。我们和我们的老朋友 Fyfe（又名 Paul Dixon）一起写了这首歌，Fyfe 是 Spector 第一次巡演的开场嘉宾，十几岁时曾与 Jed [Cullen，吉他手] 一起组成乐队，所以这是一个美好的完整时刻。”</p><p>他继续说道：“从歌词上讲，这是关于由于对他人的忠诚而与你亲近的人闹翻的故事——一种关于我们在这里所做的事情以及在不同的背景/环境/宇宙中一切会是什么样子的白日梦。我讨厌成熟这个词，但我们一定已经变老了，因为我们把原声吉他留在了里面。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="另一种生活" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fu4LqTO1D-Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>乐队的吉他手杰德·卡伦 (Jed Cullen) 补充道：“保罗 (Fyfe) 和我会在学校写歌，如果我们有勇气，就会互相询问它们是好是坏。他可能是我第一个开始谈论这个尴尬的歌曲创作问题的人。现在回想起来，很多歌曲可能都不好，但这一首是好歌。”</p><p>这首歌曲是在 LP 的主打单曲“The Notion”之后进行的，其中包含音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dev-hynes">Dev Hynes</a>的吉他独奏。这首歌曲标志着伦敦五人组 18 个月以来的第一首新音乐。</p><p>斯佩克特将开始为期九天的英国巡演，以支持《Here Come the Early Nights》。停靠站包括爱丁堡、纽卡斯尔、利兹、伯明翰、布里斯托尔、诺丁汉、南安普顿、伦敦和曼彻斯特。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fspector-tickets%2Fartist%2F1666665" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取门票并查看下面的完整日期列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cw7VDDZtXS-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" backgr